raw.question: Identified invalid GH_TOKEN blocking fallback chain
raw.chosen: Identified invalid GH_TOKEN blocking fallback chain
raw.reasoning: Reviewed trajectory traj_6mdgpdotco9m explaining git-credential-relay fallback chain. Current issue: GH_TOKEN env var is set but invalid, causing git-credential-relay to return invalid token immediately without trying other sources (hosts.yml, gh auth token, cloud API). Solution: unset GH_TOKEN to enable fallback chain.
